Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.56,IMC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow　me　Follow　you　若能相通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.40,IMC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow　me　Follow　you　无论海角天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.86,IMC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow　me　Follow　you　若能互信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:15.12,IMC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}解放这沸腾的血潮
